==Japanese==

===Etymology===
From the native Japanese word [[ます]] (to increase) merged with the corresponding Chinese character [[増]].

===Verb===
'''増す''' (ます, masu)
#to [[increase]]
:その会社の世間的な信用は来年の株式公開で増すことだろう。
:''The public confidence in the company will increase with an IPO in the coming year.''

#to [[swell]]
:昨晩からのひどい雨で川の水かさが増している。
:''The river has swollen due to heavy rain since last night.''

{{ja-go-su|増|ま|ma}}